# =============================================================================
# saas202518 - Git Ignore Configuration
# =============================================================================
# This file controls what gets committed vs ignored.
# See DEVELOPMENT-GUIDE.md for generated files policy.

# =============================================================================
# GENERATED FILES - POLICY
# =============================================================================
# ✅ DO COMMIT:
#    - fundraising/*.docx (pitch decks, investor docs)
#    - docs/*.md (documentation)
#    - package-lock.json / yarn.lock (dependency locks)
#    - .vscode/settings.json (shared editor settings)
#
# ❌ DO NOT COMMIT:
#    - .env.local (secrets)
#    - node_modules/ (dependencies)
#    - dist/, build/ (build artifacts)
#    - *.log (log files)
#
# Example: node scripts/create-pitch-deck.js → fundraising/02-PITCH-DECK.docx
#          ✅ Commit this .docx file (investor-facing document)

